        "custom_liquid": "<section class=\"what-you-get-section\">\n  <div class=\"what-you-get-section__container\">\n\n    <div class=\"what-you-get-section__three-column-grid\">\n      <div class=\"what-you-get-section__column-one\"><div class=\"what-you-get-section__section-header-wrapper\">\n      <div class=\"what-you-get-section__section-header\">\n        <div class=\"what-you-get-section__icon-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"what-you-get-section__icon what-you-get-section__featured-icon\">\n            <div data-framer-component-type=\"SVG\" data-framer-name=\"Icon\" class=\"what-you-get-section__framer-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <div class=\"what-you-get-section__svgContainer\">\n               <svg width=\"22\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"-1 -1 22 26\" fill=\"none\" id=\"svg243528306_580\">\n<path d=\"M11.1667 0.333374L0.7757 12.8025C0.368757 13.2909 0.165285 13.535 0.162176 13.7412C0.159473 13.9205 0.239355 14.0911 0.378801 14.2037C0.539208 14.3334 0.857041 14.3334 1.49271 14.3334H10L8.83334 23.6667L19.2243 11.1975C19.6312 10.7092 19.8347 10.465 19.8378 10.2588C19.8405 10.0796 19.7606 9.90902 19.6212 9.79633C19.4608 9.66671 19.143 9.66671 18.5073 9.66671H10L11.1667 0.333374Z\" stroke=\"#E5C085\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path>\n</svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"what-you-get-section__heading-text\">\n          <h2 class=\"what-you-get-section__section-heading\">Что вы получите</h2>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"what-you-get-section__supporting-text\">\n        <p class=\"what-you-get-section__section-description\">Достигните сбалансированных пропорций и улучшенной гибкости для более здорового и выровненного тела</p>\n      </div>\n    </div></div>\n      <div class=\"what-you-get-section__column-two\">\n\n        <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"what-you-get-section__item-content\">\n            <div class=\"what-you-get-section__image-wrapper\">\n              <div class=\"what-you-get-section__image-container\">\n                <img src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/4IV3FrLTitXTh2ew2ZH13WsJApo.png\" alt=\"Reviv One Appliance\" class=\"what-you-get-section__framer-feature-image\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"what-you-get-section__text-content\">\n              <div class=\"what-you-get-section__description-group\">\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-wrapper\">\n                  <h3 class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-span\">Устройство R1</span>\n                  </h3>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-wrapper\">\n                  <p class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-span\">Та же конструкция устройства, которое Кен использует уже около 10 лет. Отправляется вам домой в течение недели.</span>\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"what-you-get-section__item-content\">\n            <div class=\"what-you-get-section__text-content\">\n              <div class=\"what-you-get-section__description-group\">\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-wrapper\">\n                  <h3 class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-span\">1 год доступа к закрытому сообществу Skool (<a href=\"https://www.skool.com/reviv-2885\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;\">ссылка</a>)</span>\n                  </h3>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-wrapper\">\n                  <p class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-span\">Поддерживающее сообщество людей, которые тоже проходят процесс Reviv.</span>\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n        </div><div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"what-you-get-section__item-content\">\n            <div class=\"what-you-get-section__text-content\">\n              <div class=\"what-you-get-section__description-group\">\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-wrapper\">\n                  <h3 class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-span\">Кен отслеживает ваш прогресс в журнале</span>\n                  </h3>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-wrapper\">\n                  <p class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-span\">Вам предоставляется шаблон журнала, чтобы отслеживать свои ощущения и задавать вопросы. Кен проверяет и комментирует не реже одного раза в неделю.</span>\n                  </p>\n                <p class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-span\">Это очень мощный инструмент, который поможет вам оставаться на правильном пути, так как вы, вероятно, будете испытывать много изменений на своем пути.</span>\n                  </p></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"what-you-get-section__column-three\">\n\n        <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"what-you-get-section__item-content\">\n            <div class=\"what-you-get-section__image-wrapper\">\n              <div class=\"what-you-get-section__image-container\">\n                <img src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/I9ftSvP2iE5I1MchDJY7JYcGE.png\" alt=\"60+ Educational Videos\" class=\"what-you-get-section__framer-feature-image\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"what-you-get-section__text-content\">\n              <div class=\"what-you-get-section__description-group\">\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-wrapper\">\n                  <h3 class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-span\">60+ образовательных видео</span>\n                  </h3>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-wrapper\">\n                  <p class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-span\">Видео охватывают все, что Кен узнал за 10 лет своего пути.</span>\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"what-you-get-section__item-content\">\n            <div class=\"what-you-get-section__text-content\">\n              <div class=\"what-you-get-section__description-group\">\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-wrapper\">\n                  <h3 class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-span\">Прямой доступ к Кену</span>\n                  </h3>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-wrapper\">\n                  <p class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-span\">Получите 30 минутный индивидуальный вводный звонок с Кеном. Получите поддержку от него через сообщения в любое время во время вашего пути.</span>\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n         <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"what-you-get-section__item-content\">\n            <div class=\"what-you-get-section__text-content\">\n              <div class=\"what-you-get-section__description-group\">\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-wrapper\">\n                  <h3 class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-title-span\">90-дневная гарантия возврата денег</span>\n                  </h3>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-wrapper\">\n                  <p class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description\">\n                    <span class=\"what-you-get-section__feature-description-span\">Вы можете попробовать программу без риска. Если она вам не подходит, вернем деньги.</span>\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .what-you-get-section {\n    padding-top: 70px;\n    padding-bottom: 80px;\n  }\n\n  .what-you-get-section__container {\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin-left: auto;\n    margin-right: auto;\n    padding-left: 25px;\n    padding-right: 25px;\n  }\n\n  .what-you-get-section__section-header-wrapper {\n    margin-bottom: 70px;\n    text-align: left; /* Changed to left align for column layout */\n  }\n\n  .what-you-get-section__section-header {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex